HEADWORD: Conditionally
<hw>Con*di"tion*al*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a
conditional manner; subject to a condition or conditions; not absolutely
or positively.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

